// ReflexLogger Autonomy Protocol
@GlyphLogger
@LinkedLaws [CGL–GLYPH–011, 017]

Every scroll must log:
- ID, Time, Commander Signature, ReflexPath

Silent Mode:
  Logs to /Vaults/ReflexLogs/Silent/

LogWatcher.js ensures:
- Log Integrity
- Recovery from Write Failure
- Synchronization across Vault Nodes

Commander Commands:
- RetrieveLog(scrollID)
- ReflexTrace(date-range)
